SEARCH
Package emissary.parser

Class NIOSessionParser

java.lang.Object
emissary.parser.SessionParser
emissary.parser.NIOSessionParser
Direct Known Subclasses:
FillingNIOParser, SimpleNioParser
public abstract class NIOSessionParser extends SessionParser
Provide a basic NIO-based session parser that reads data in chunks from the underlying channel. A chunk might have zero or more complete sessions within it. The chunk buffer will begin at minChunkSize, but grow as large as maxChunkSize in order to accomodate a complete session. Sessions larger than maxChunkSize will lead to ParserExceptions
